  {
    "uuid": "25b7b40c-5e81-577e-bd82-9dc670f3f8e9",
    "entry": "草房",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "そうぼう",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "thatched hut",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "あとの一人は、この二人からずつと離れて、打麦場の隅にある草房の軒下に立つてゐる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "酒虫",
                "author": "芥川龍之介",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "見ると、木曾｜御岳山下百草房　　　　奈良井屋大蔵　とあるので、「――あああなた様が」　と別当は見上げて、ゆうべからの粗略を、かえすがえす口惜しげに詫び入った。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "宮本武蔵",
                "author": "空の巻",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "relations": {
